              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="info-3 grid__item one-third">
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <img
                  src="//digital-world-8.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/changing-money_100x_crop_center.png?v=1613508275"
                  alt=""
                >
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <span class="h4">30 days return</span>

                <span class="h5"
                  >A year after the first generation took the smartwatch world by storm with its timeless looks</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="info-4 grid__item one-third">
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <img
                  src="//digital-world-8.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/medal_1_100x_crop_center.png?v=1613508275"
                  alt=""
                >
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <span class="h4">Best Quality products</span>

                <span class="h5"
                  >A year after the first generation took the smartwatch world by storm with its timeless looks</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-5 grid__item one-third">
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <img
                  src="//digital-world-8.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/piggy-bank_100x_crop_center.png?v=1613508275"
                  alt=""
                >
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <span class="h4">Saving your money</span>
                <span class="h5"
                  >A year after the first generation took the smartwatch world by storm with its timeless looks</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-6 grid__item one-third">
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-icon">
                <img
                  src="//digital-world-8.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/delivery-truck_1_100x_crop_center.png?v=1613508275"
                  alt=""
                >
              </div>
              <div class="info-text">
                <span class="h4">Free delivery from $50</span>
